©TAMARA AKOPIAN
SPENT MANY QUEIT[SIC] MOMENTS SITTING HERE
DONATED BY HER DAUGHTER NELLY AND MANY
FRIENDS IN PIMLICO IN HONOUR OF HER UNIQUE
SPIRIT OF LOVE AND BEAUTY"≤
ĮKENNETH NELSON
1930         (ACTOR)          1993    
(TEXAS)                          (LONDON)
       Life was FANTASTIC      
                                      NAOMI"Ķ
≤Dedicated to Both Our Angels who fell Asleep in Our Arms,
Ms Simin Eftekharzadeh & Mr Hossein Kavakeb
26th November 2013 & 12th July 2016.
Thank You for Blessing Our Lives
with Your Energy, Love, Strength & Imagination.
We are honoured to have had You Both in Our Lives
and We Love & Miss You Dearly."Ĺ
ļIn memory of
Derek Lane
From a select number of friends who spent many happy
hours in his company and together enjoyed the splendour
of this city and the tranquility of these gardens"Ņ
