ĺFrom Phil to Alina, my wife and love of my life.
For memories of lunches and moments shared
in Berkeley Square Mayfair and in
the London Town that we grew to love together
and call our home."ŕ
◊In memory of
William, Marquess of Hartington
Coldstream Guards
Killed in action whilst serving with 5th Battalion
Belgium September 1944
This seat is given by his brother and sisters
Andrew, Elizabeth and Anne"‹
